wdi2-TM.TAX.MRCH.SM.AR.ZS.def: Simple mean applied tariff is the unweighted average of effectively applied rates for all products subject to tariffs calculated for all traded goods.
wdi2-TM.TAX.MRCH.SM.AR.ZS.name: Tariff rate, applied, simple mean
wdi2-TM.TAX.MRCH.SM.AR.ZS.source: World Bank staff estimates using the World Integrated Trade Solution system, based on data from United Nations Conference on Trade and Development's Trade Analysis and Information System (TRAINS) database and the World Trade Organization’s (WTO) Integrated Data Base (IDB) and Consolidated Tariff Schedules (CTS) database.
